audio.name: Puoro & Oro...
audio.description: Ka uta hihiri i te ororongo.
audio.info-controls: Takahuri i te kitenga o ngā mana pāpāho.
audio.info-autoplay: Ki te pono, ka purei te pāpāho ina tāuru tuatahi i te tirohanga.
audio.info-synchronize: Ki te pono, ka tukutahitia te pāpāho ki ngā kiritaki tūhono katoa.
audio.info-loop: Mēnā e pono ana ka koromeke te pāpāho mō ake tonu atu.
audio.info-distanceModel: I whakamahia te hātepe papatono hei tatau i te rārangi ororongo.
audio.info-rolloffFactor: Ko tētahi uara taurua e whakamārama ana i te tere o te whakaiti i te rōrahi i te nekehanga atu o te pūtake i te kaiwhakarongo. 0 ki te 1
audio.info-rfInfinity: Ko tētahi uara taurua e whakamārama ana i te tere o te whakaiti i te rōrahi i te nekehanga atu o te pūtake i te kaiwhakarongo. 0 ki te Infinity
audio.info-refDistance: Ko tētahi uara taurua e tohu ana i te tawhiti tohutoro hei whakaiti i te rōrahi i te nekehanga atu o te pūtake ororongo mai i te kaiwhakarongo.
audio.info-maxDistance: Ko tētahi uara taurua e tohu ana i te tawhiti mōrahi i waenga i te pūtake ororongo me te kaiwhakarongo, ā muri ake nei kāore te rōrahi i whakahekea anōtia.
audio.info-coneInnerAngle: Ko tētahi uara taurua e whakamārama ana i te koki, i roto i ngā waeine, o tētahi kōkā i roto, ā, kāore he whakaiti rōrahi.
audio.info-coneOuterAngle: Ko tētahi uara taurua e whakamārama ana i te koki, i roto i ngā waeine, o tētahi kōkā i waho ka whakahekea te rōrahi e tētahi uara taimau, e tautuhia ana e te huanga coneOuterGain.
audio.info-coreOuterGain: Ko tētahi uara taurua e whakamārama ana i te nui o te whakaiti rōrahi i waho o te kone i tautuhia e te huanga coneOuterAngle. Ko tōna uara taunoa ko te 0, ko te tikanga kāore he oro e rangona.

performance.title: Taki Mahinga
performance.info-polycount: E tūtohu ana mātou kia kaua tō tirohanga e whakamahi i ngā tapatoru neke atu i te 50,000 mō ngā pūrere pūkoro.
performance.info-material: E tūtohu ana mātou kia kaua e nui ake i te 25 ngā rauemi ahurei i tō tirohanga hei whakaiti i ngā waea tātuhi ki ngā pūrere pūkoro.
performance.info-texture: E tūtohu ana mātou kia kaua ō kanokano e whakamahi neke atu i te 256MB o te RAM ataata mō ngā pūrere pūkoro. E tūtohu ana hoki mātou ki te whakamahi i ngā kanokano nui ake i te 2048 x 2048.
performance.info-lights: Ahakoa kāore e whakahohea ngā rama hihiri ki ngā pūrere pūkoro, e tūtohu ana mātou mā te whakamahi i ngā rama neke atu i te 3 i tō tirohanga (tae atu ki ngā rama āpiti me ngā rama hemisphere) kia whakahaere ai tō tirohanga i ngā RW mutunga hahaka.
performance.info-fileSize: E tūtohu ana mātou i tētahi rahi kōnae whakamutunga kāore i neke atu i te 16MB mō ngā tūhononga hōkaiipurangi hahaka. Mā te whakaiti i te rahi kōnae e whakaiti i te wā hei tikiake i tō tirohanga.
